Package pl.edu.agh.kis.lab.pz1.game_logic.texas

Interface HandRanker

All Known Implementing Classes:
ClassicHandRanker
public interface HandRanker
Interface defining a contract for ranking the hands of players in a Texas Hold'em game. Implementations of this interface will determine the winner(s) based on the players' hands and community cards.

  • Method Details

    • pickWinner

      List<THPlayer> pickWinner(List<THPlayer> players, CommunityCards communityCards)
      Picks the winner(s) from the list of players based on their hands and the community cards. The winner is determined by comparing the hand rankings according to the rules of Texas Hold'em.
      Parameters:
      players - A list of players whose hands are to be evaluated.
      communityCards - The community cards shared by all players.
      Returns:
      A list of players who have the best hand(s).
